beer.beer_description: Golden-yellow and bright, with 32 bitter units and quite hoppy compared to most of the other Pils our Weihenstephaner Pils comes up with a distinctive aroma of hops with a pleasant bitterness. This combination provides a balanced mix and guarantees great enjoyment. Brewed according to our centuries-old brewing tradition on the Weihenstephan hill.
